    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      387.98,
      525.57,
      451.78
    ],
    "text": "On the evening of 20.05.2026, the Seeduwa Police Station commenced an investigation following information received that a foul odour was emanating from a house located in the Mukalangamuwa area within the Seeduwa Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      466.36,
      524.67,
      497.98
    ],
    "text": "Subsequent inspections carried out at the residence led to the discovery of the body of a woman concealed inside a suitcase kept in a bedroom.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      512.56,
      426.0,
      544.18
    ],
    "text": "The deceased was identified as a 79-year-old resident of Mukalangamuwa, Seeduwa.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      558.76,
      516.26,
      622.57
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the deceased had been living alone at the residence. It was further uncovered that the CCTV cameras installed at the house had been removed and the telephone lines had been severed.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      637.15,
      523.29,
      749.31
    ],
    "text": "A magisterial inquiry and post-mortem examination were scheduled to be conducted on 21.05.2026. Further investigations are being carried out by the Seeduwa Police to apprehend the suspects involved.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      31.82,
      354.49,
      64.63
    ],
