      466.24,
      329.5,
      481.78
    ],
    "text": "Murder \u2013 Grandpass Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      496.36,
      521.26,
      560.14
    ],
    "text": "On the night of 20.05.2026, the Grandpass Police Station launched an investigation following reports that a man had been fatally assaulted with a sharp weapon in the Fergusson Road area within the Grandpass Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
