      493.7,
      606.37
    ],
    "text": "The deceased was identified as a 31-year-old resident of the Modara Uyana apartment complex.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
