      107.42,
      350.78,
      507.15,
      414.58
    ],
    "text": "Investigations were initiated at the Uhana Police Station following information received on the afternoon of 20.05.2026 that a person who had gone bathing in a canal in the Dematamalpalessa area within the Uhana Police Division had drowned.",
