    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      545.56,
      520.27,
      609.49
    ],
    "text": "On the morning of 20.05.2026, a motorcycle travelling towards Kethsirigama along the Damana\u2013Kethsirigama Road, near the Third Bridge within the Damana Police Division, collided with a van travelling ahead while attempting to overtake it.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      623.95,
      503.76,
      671.77
    ],
    "text": "The motorcyclist and the pillion rider sustained serious injuries in the accident and were admitted to the Ampara Hospital for treatment. The pillion rider later succumbed to injuries while receiving treatment.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      686.35,
      477.25,
      701.89
    ],
    "text": "The deceased was identified as a 25-year-old resident of Elpitiya.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
